import { Component, OnInit } from '@angular/core'; import { ActivatedRoute, Params } from '@angular/router'; @Component({ selector: 'app-catalogo', templateUrl: './catalogo.component.html', styleUrls: ['./catalogo.component.css'] }) export class CatalogoComponent implements OnInit { inicio!: {navcatalogo: string}; constructor(private rutaActiva: ActivatedRoute) {} ngOnInit() { this.inicio = { navcatalogo: this.rutaActiva.snapshot.params['navcatalogo'], }; this.rutaActiva.params.subscribe( (params: Params) => { this.inicio['navcatalogo'] = params['navcatalogo']; } ); } }
